Package: bnns
Title: Bayesian Neural Network with Stan
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Swarnendu", "Chatterjee", , "swarnendu.stat@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Provides a flexible formula-based interface for building and training Bayesian Neural Networks (BNNs) using Stan. Enables users to model complex relationships while quantifying uncertainty through posterior distributions. Suitable for applications in domains such as clinical trials, finance, and other areas requiring interpretable Bayesian predictions.
